OL,5, An "unprecedented shortage" of the     
OL,6, heroin substitute diamorphine in       
OL,7, England is putting hundreds of lives at
OL,8, risk, say drug workers.                
OL,10,FDiamorphine is a pharmaceutical form of
OL,11,Fheroin prescribed when methadone and   
OL,12,Fother medications are ineffective.     
OL,14,FFormer heroin users have told the BBC  
OL,15,Fthey have relapsed for the first time  
OL,16,Fin decades as a result of the shortage.
OL,18,FDoctors say the problem is also        
OL,19,Faffecting some end-of-life patients who
OL,20,Fare given diamorphine for pain relief. 
